{"tid":751073,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排又少左人Hi 臭CITY","createTime":"2018-07-21T13:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:29:50.000Z","uid":137555,"like":27,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"141247aad77f7205db538cda599e3a62da13e52f","tid":751073,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:50:44.000Z","msg":"首先,Hi臭city o 既風氣,由4月尾至6月中會達至高峰， <br />\n因為班DSE面對放榜壓力無從發洩 <br />\n要搵人黎踩下定下個心 <br />\n6月中後會突然水盡鵝飛 <br />\n一黎怕自己會入，留條後路 <br />\n二黎開始迷信，想積下口德 <br />\n<br />\nDSE放榜後，愁雲慘霧 <br />\n班中3仔見狀都唔敢亂Hi <br />\n所以由6月尾至8月 <br />\n情況相若，風氣極低位橫行，如經濟衰退一樣 <br />\n<br />\n到9月，開學兩三禮拜，新一屆DSE 中3仔開始有壓力，想搵人踩 <br />\nretake緊o既又想有野俾佢增強信心，又踩 <br />\n讀緊asso ive 跟唔上o個班/讀得唔開心o既，又踩 <br />\n因此9月會有個小陽春，之後橫行， <br />\n12月至1月頭，同2月中，分別都會有個小陽春，因為有假放得閒，同考試迫近， <br />\n壓力愈來愈大，3月至4月頭會一直高位橫行 <br />\n<br />\n最後又到4月尾高峰 <br />\n年年都如是，歲歲皆如此 <br />\n<br />\n股市係咁就好囉Hi 你 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/215041_d4b9641bc2cb49d914e05e87aa8bd5b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F215041_d4b9641bc2cb49d914e05e87aa8bd5b8.jpg&h=e6494f58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac3d85408553c11f0c336cefedc9b0e5bf7c800e","tid":751073,"uid":2419,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"Hi你老母"},{"pid":"26776e2de6eb9a0a032421535751dd4a97281a66","tid":751073,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:56:05.000Z","msg":"每年都要LOOP一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9347a2e26f04354d24d3b2577b60086e93469ac4","tid":751073,"uid":171509,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"大家hi hi hi"},{"pid":"a3874bb49cde3a3ab5891b1aa50f09df4bda5af5","tid":751073,"uid":193804,"like":19,"dislike":13,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:59:05.000Z","msg":"shitty仔9成都廢<br />\n收勁多asshole之餘 dse收分都好低"},{"pid":"ab43bae